metadata.name: All The Way #6
metadata.description:
"All the Way" is a visually stunning and dynamic generative art piece that is sure to make a striking addition to any art collection. Created using the programming language p5js, this artwork is truly one of a kind and cannot be replicated.

The vibrant colors, fluid shapes, and dynamic movement in "All the Way" make it an ideal centerpiece for any space. The constantly shifting shapes and colors create a sense of energy and motion that will draw the eye and captivate the viewer. This piece is perfect for anyone who loves abstract art or is looking for something unique and eye-catching to add to their collection.

Additionally, the theme of "All the Way" is one that is sure to resonate with many people. The artwork represents the flow of life, the power of creativity, and the endless possibilities that exist in the world around us. This makes it an ideal choice for anyone who values personal growth, exploration, and a sense of adventure.

Whether you're an art collector, an art enthusiast, or simply someone who appreciates beautiful and thought-provoking art, "All the Way" is a must-have addition to your collection. With its dynamic and abstract style, this piece is sure to spark conversations and inspire new ideas. Don't miss out on the chance to own a truly unique and captivating artwork that you will enjoy for years to come!

To save image press "s"
To save image in high quality add &print=2 or &print=3 in the live URL then press "s".

Note: Image can take a minute to render.

Created using p5js and p5js pattern
Created By Winston
Feb 2023

metadata.name: Serene Garden #150
metadata.description:
A Serene Garden is a peaceful and tranquil outdoor space designed to evoke feelings of calm and relaxation.

The overall design and atmosphere of a Serene Garden encourage reflection and contemplation, making it a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of daily life. It's a place where visitors can slow down, breathe deeply, and reconnect with nature. Whether through the gentle sound of a fountain, the fragrance of blooming flowers, or the rustle of leaves in the wind, a serene garden provides a sensory escape that soothes the mind and nourishes the soul.

As a features, there are 17 color palettes for flowers, beautifull handpicked gradient backgounds whitch are mixing with flower palettes and together gives pleasing expirience of render/output.

To download high quality image, open 'Live' and press "S" to save 2500x1800px



February 2023
Made with P5js

metadata.name: On Time #168
metadata.description:
[ CLICK TO START THE SOUND ]

Often, I find myself feeling like I'm running behind, or that time is slipping away too quickly. I struggle to be present in the moment because of anxieties related to the past or the future.

"On Time" explores the elusive nature of time and my relationship with it. Through this project, I aimed to create an experience that captures the way that we each experience time in our own way. Seeing that time is not linear but instead, it ebbs and flows in different ways.

At the heart of the experience is a visual reminder to stay in the moment and embrace it. The project consists of 256 unique visuals, each one representing a fleeting moment that has been captured in digital form. These moments are presented in a way that allows you to observe them, appreciate them, and stay present in them. "On Time" is an invitation to pause, take a deep breath, and remind ourselves that we are always where we need to be.

Controls
[ f ] - fullscreen
[ s ] - save the current frame as an image

Dance of many legs. Moving fast knows that nothing can forever last. For if it stops, it meets its end, no pause allowed.
